- 7d true-boundary reset path now re-enters `_init_session`; when warm-up is enabled, that GPU work is serialized under `inference_lock`.

**Default Preservation**
When `NEMOTRON_WARMUP_MS` is unset or empty, `session_warmup_ms == 0`; no warm-up branch runs, no per-session warm-up log is emitted, reset paths stay synchronous as before, and the timeline offset is `+0`. `NEMOTRON_FINALIZE_SILENCE_MS` default remains `150`.

